comments: Green (OKC) engages and disengages with Adams (OKC) as Adams moves to set the pick.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
McLemore (HOU) does not intentionally kick the ball as Paul (OKC) dribbles the ball off of McLemore's right foot.
After the ball touches McLemore's (HOU) foot, Paul (OKC) splits his feet as he re-starts his dribble.
Paul (OKC) briefly has his off-arm on McLemore's (HOU) body before quickly removing it.
McLemore (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position and moves in a direct path as he absorbs the contact from Paul (OKC) during the drive.
Harden (HOU) maintains a rested left hand on Adams' (OKC) backside as Adams receives the pass and quickly removes it as Adams starts his upward shooting motion.
House (HOU) brushes Adams' (OKC) body as marginal contact occurs during his layup attempt.
Tucker (HOU) delivers contact to Schroder's (OKC) side, which dislodges him from his legally obtained rebounding position.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is established in Harden's (HOU) path as marginal contact occurs at the end of his drive.
Green (HOU) avoids making contact with Paul (OKC) after his gather.
Adams (OKC) rests his left hand on Gordon's (HOU) side as marginal contact occurs during Gordon's drive into the lane.
Video evidence is inconclusive in determining if Paul (OKC) makes any contact with Harden's (HOU) left arm as he is passing.
Schroder (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as contact occurs with House (HOU) along the sideline.
House Jr. (HOU) is the last player to touch the ball after his right foot steps out of bounds along the sideline.
Harden (OKC) establishes legal guarding position in Paul's (OKC) path and absorbs the body contact that occurs following the pick.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that the contact first initiated by Paul (OKC) on Harden (HOU) occurred prior to the release of the inbound pass.
Schroder (OKC) wraps his right arm across the front of Gordon's (HOU) body, which dislodges him during the inbound.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined Tucker (HOU) passed the ball out of bounds with no players from either team touching it.
Gallinari (OKC) and Tucker (HOU) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Green (HOU) briefly has his arm around Dort's (OKC) upper half before correcting.
Dort (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in Green's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
Prior to the timeout being awarded, Dort (OKC) and Harden (HOU) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Noel (OKC) extends his leg into House Jr.'s (HOU) path and trips House Jr. after he receives the pass.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in Green's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
Harden (HOU) is retreating in his defensive position as marginal contact occurs with Paul's (OKC) front/side during the drive.
Harden (HOU) brushes Paul's (OKC) back with his hand after Paul's gather and does not apply any force.
